{"tid":1251751,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非 勇武 和解Post","createTime":"2019-06-22T16:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T20:59:56.000Z","uid":101824,"like":83,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"93a14a8d2de03e7f0231ddc1c3717aec7562dce9","tid":1251751,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:18:33.000Z","msg":"眼見咁多Post捉鬼，又嘈嚟嘈去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家仲記得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同時間，聽下大家意見，諗清楚原因。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就621琴日所見<br />\n<br />\n和理非方面：<br />\n唔應該：邊個衝邊個就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該：衝咗警總，只係送死，警犬人手物資都夠哂，同埋入你嘅罪名更大。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而且冇實際作用</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁到底勇武，實際作用係啲咩呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好重要 好重要 好重要</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係要拎嚟同政府談判嘅籌碼。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然，佔警總就真係冇可能。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其他地方，例如大家講嘅政府Office地方 都係唔錯嘅選擇，可以癱瘓政府運作。但一定要<span style=\"font-size: large;\">長時間</span>佔領，令佢地做唔到嘢，先可以令雙方<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有機會</span>談判。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而之前點解要話佔領立法會呢？</span><br />\n就係因為佔領咗立會，立法/其他程序無法進行/通過，短時間已經對政府運作有大影響。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\">雖然同柒婆冇咩好談判 因為對方唔會咁易罷休 但談判失敗之後 就係一個好時機去令行動升級</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以 武勇嘅人都要記住：<br />\n唔應該：係又衝唔係又衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該：向<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可信</span>嘅人解釋計劃 組織一班人 諗下點衝 衝完後果 衝完成功可以得到嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我相信喺得呢度嘅人，都有自己思考能力，所以大家更加應該溝通多啲，而唔係收收埋埋。</span><br />\n<br />\n以下開放大家討論。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee2603dd2ea99074cbe7a88c66e97d2c9ebcf1f","tid":1251751,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"71b5ae0c6476389df051c8d502cc16fc4c862bd0","tid":1251751,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8afdfe6c65507243fe305853ac38cb27b2e24f96","tid":1251751,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af52d919846f3d7ecc02adafc47b1b6776e65a71","tid":1251751,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:30:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b3d95075b6df192e3288a7c1d3b39d62aab9c595","tid":1251751,"uid":101824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8afdfe6c65507243fe305853ac38cb27b2e24f96","tid":1251751,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:38:18.000Z","msg":"要試下慢慢走出自己Comfort Zone<br />\n同埋要注意幾樣嘢<br />\n1. 裝備 你唔full gear上陣嘅話 棧搞<br />\n2. 留意消息/睇人群 唔好落單"},{"pid":"2af64748cada2e9f9b53b70db7d92b3ea3d4515f","tid":1251751,"uid":262340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"026f74021c807defd98afecfccd9cfdbc3979e4c","tid":1251751,"uid":165336,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:55:01.000Z","msg":"講左好多次，邊度都搞得唯獨狗屋唔搞得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n圍下已經極限，你一衝有權屈你搶武裝搞政變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時名正言順實彈鎮壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎多次64，全世界冇一個國家幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358f5f8ad83c47b3cf7cbd80ffc3451754e94f98","tid":1251751,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:37:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1f044ae683aee24f6d52f1226d819f16e0f7bdf1","tid":1251751,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:47:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"df9a9ca692e587495ee859df6a84953a06872197","tid":1251751,"uid":265467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:48:17.000Z","msg":"Sorry ,借位一用<br />\n<br />\n大家應該由問題根源去思考,與其一樣樣去反對政府D賣港政策,點解唔用真普選趕走曬班賣港賊,必須要令更多人知問題根源核心,個個支持真普選!!!<br />\n<br />\n一日無真普選,建制派,港共政權賣港賊一車車補上,要徹底趕走賣港賊,只有真普選!!!<br />\n<br />\n[請廣傳]香港只有真普選先可以趕走港共政府同建制派賣港賊!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251736</a>"},{"pid":"c024f06aec150d6cffff39e040a194b699c7547e","tid":1251751,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccd40cc93dbea3d502fc0c7fb0aef09a8370e59","tid":1251751,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ceb984451b8b2cd7981b5d3794f9bfe6d7f4a3f","tid":1251751,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:15:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db0a1e968817dd75ae720569969cc19214940bbe","tid":1251751,"uid":34119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:16:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">遍地開花</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">各有各法</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"42aa50e0afe788f6f7220b89e5a16cbc48d0e5ec","tid":1251751,"uid":14305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8afdfe6c65507243fe305853ac38cb27b2e24f96","tid":1251751,"ui